meta {
  name: Module Icon
  type: http
  seq: 4
}

get {
  url: {{assetUrl}}/operator/modules/uniequip_002_amiya.png
  body: none
  auth: none
}

docs {
  Module icon image. Path segment is value.modules[i].info.uniEquipId from the operator document.
  uniEquipId format: uniequip_NNN_operatorname (e.g. uniequip_002_amiya).
  Replace the hardcoded ID in the URL to test different modules.
  Displayed in the Modules tab of the /op command.
}
